text: TV6 (in ) is the sixth Algerian public national television channel. It is part of the state-owned EPTV group, along with TV1, Canal Algérie, TV3, TV4, TV5 and TV7. It is an Arab language channel.TV 6 is directed to the Algerian families. ==History== TV6 was launched on 26 March 2020. == References == ==External links== * * Category:Arab mass media Category:Television stations in Algeria Category:Television channels and stations established in 2020
title: TV6 (Algerian TV channel)
